<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>Aryadhar Gupta — Driver, Builder & Engineering Creator</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Aryadhar Gupta is a motorsport driver, builder, engineering creator, CAD user, IoT maker, and climate activist based in Delhi, India."
    />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#07111f" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #07111f;
        --bg-deep: #050b14;
        --surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
        --surface-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.085);
        --surface-soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);

        --text: #f2f7ff;
        --muted: #a9b7ca;
        --quiet: #728197;

        --accent: #67e8f9;
        --accent-strong: #38bdf8;
        --accent-soft: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.12);

        --radius-sm: 12px;
        --radius-md: 18px;
        --radius-lg: 28px;

        --max-width: 1180px;
        --shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18), transparent 34rem),
          radial-gradient(circle at 82% 12%, rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.1), transparent 30rem),
          linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, #08111f 48%, var(--bg-deep) 100%);
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }

      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.026) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.026) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 48px 48px;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45), transparent 70%);
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      p,
      h1,
      h2,
      h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .wrap {
        width: min(100% - 32px, var(--max-width));
        margin-inline: auto;
      }

      .nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 20;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: rgba(7, 17, 31, 0.76);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.35);
      }

      .nav-inner {
        min-height: 72px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      }

      .brand-mark {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
        color: #03111c;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.08);
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .nav-cta {
        padding: 9px 13px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
        color: var(--text) !important;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 96px 0 72px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(320px, 0.85fr);
        gap: 34px;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        width: fit-content;
        margin-bottom: 22px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.24);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.075);
        color: #d4fbff;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        font-weight: 750;
      }

      .eyebrow-dot {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.9);
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 860px;
        margin-bottom: 22px;
        font-size: clamp(3.15rem, 7vw, 6.55rem);
        line-height: 0.92;
        letter-spacing: -0.078em;
      }

      .lead {
        max-width: 760px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 2vw, 1.28rem);
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 32px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 46px;
        padding: 0 17px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 750;
        transition:
          transform 180ms ease,
          border-color 180ms ease,
          background 180ms ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        border-color: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.42);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.085);
      }

      .btn-primary {
        border-color: transparent;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
        color: #03111c;
      }

      .panel {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.032)),
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .hero-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        width: 280px;
        height: 280px;
        top: -120px;
        right: -120px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.16);
        filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .hero-card-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .label {
        color: var(--quiet);
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        font-weight: 850;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .hero-card h2 {
        margin: 12px 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.55rem;
        line-height: 1.15;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .hero-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .profile-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0;
        margin-top: 26px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .profile-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 14px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .profile-row span:first-child {
        color: var(--quiet);
      }

      .profile-row span:last-child {
        font-weight: 750;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .proof-strip {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 42px;
      }

      .proof-card {
        min-height: 112px;
        padding: 17px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.043);
      }

      .proof-card strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      }

      .proof-card span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--quiet);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 86px 0;
      }

      .section-head {
        display: flex;
        align-items: end;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .kicker {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        font-weight: 850;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h2.section-title {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        max-width: 760px;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.6vw, 3.45rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      }

      .section-note {
        max-width: 455px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.82fr;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .content-card {
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .content-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .content-card p + p {
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .quote-card {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100%;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .quote-mark {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 3.8rem;
        line-height: 0.8;
      }

      blockquote {
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
        font-weight: 850;
        line-height: 1.12;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .quote-card p {
        margin-top: 26px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .tag-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 30px;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        color: #dce8f7;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .capability-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .capability-card {
        min-height: 275px;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .number {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border: 1px solid rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.22);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .capability-card h3,
      .project-card h3,
      .timeline-card h3,
      .press-card h3 {
        margin: 20px 0 9px;
        font-size: 1.16rem;
        line-height: 1.22;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .capability-card p,
      .project-card p,
      .timeline-card p,
      .press-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .project-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .project-card {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 405px;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .project-visual {
        height: 136px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-end;
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
        border-radius: 20px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 24% 20%, rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.28), transparent 10rem),
          radial-gradient(circle at 82% 80%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18), transparent 9rem),
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      }

      .project-visual span {
        color: rgba(242, 247, 255, 0.82);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 850;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .project-card .tag-row {
        margin-top: auto;
      }

      .project-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .text-link {
        color: #cffafe;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }

      .timeline {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .timeline-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 126px 1fr;
        gap: 22px;
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .year {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .timeline-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .press-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .press-card {
        padding: 26px;
      }

      .press-links {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .media-placeholder {
        min-height: 300px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 34px;
        border: 1px dashed rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.28);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        background: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.045);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .media-placeholder strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      }

      .media-placeholder span {
        display: block;
        max-width: 590px;
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .contact-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
        gap: 28px;
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .contact-card .section-title {
        max-width: 440px;
      }

      .contact-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .contact-item {
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
      }

      .contact-item span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--quiet);
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 850;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .contact-item a,
      .contact-item strong {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 6px;
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 750;
        text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 28px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--quiet);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .footer-inner {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1040px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .about-grid,
        .contact-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .proof-strip,
        .capability-grid,
        .project-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }

        .press-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .nav-inner {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
          padding: 16px 0;
        }

        .nav-links {
          width: 100%;
          overflow-x: auto;
          padding-bottom: 2px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 680px) {
        .wrap {
          width: min(100% - 24px, var(--max-width));
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 64px 0 46px;
        }

        .section {
          padding: 62px 0;
        }

        .proof-strip,
        .capability-grid,
        .project-grid,
        .contact-list {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .timeline-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 16vw, 4.15rem);
        }

        .section-head {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .content-card,
        .quote-card,
        .contact-card {
          padding: 22px;
        }

        .profile-row {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .profile-row span:last-child {
          text-align: left;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="wrap nav-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="Aryadhar Gupta homepage">
          <span class="brand-mark">AG</span>
          <span>Aryadhar Gupta</span>
        </a>

        <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary navigation">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#capabilities">Capabilities</a>
          <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
          <a href="#timeline">Timeline</a>
          <a href="#press">Press</a>
          <a class="nav-cta" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="hero-grid">
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow">
                <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
                Driver • Builder • Creator
              </div>

              <h1>Engineering speed into real-world systems.</h1>

              <p class="lead">
                I work across motorsport, mechanical systems, CAD, connected
                hardware, and climate-focused leadership — combining track
                experience with hands-on technical execution.
              </p>

              <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#projects">View Projects</a>
                <a class="btn" href="#contact">Start a Conversation</a>
              </div>

              <div class="proof-strip" aria-label="Key credibility markers">
                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>Formula-4 Testing</strong>
                  <span>Driver development and circuit experience.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>Drift Instructor</strong>
                  <span>BAD BOI DRIFTS, car control and coaching.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>UNO Minda</strong>
                  <span>Product Integration & Market Analysis.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>2nd at BIC</strong>
                  <span>Autocross result at Buddh International Circuit.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>CAD Since 2016</strong>
                  <span>Design, prototyping, fixtures and mechanisms.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="proof-card">
                  <strong>Mensa Member</strong>
                  <span>Analytical problem-solving and fast learning.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="panel hero-card">
              <div class="hero-card-content">
                <div class="label">Current Focus</div>
                <h2>Building a serious technical and motorsport profile.</h2>
                <p>
                  This site is designed as a professional base for racing
                  opportunities, sponsorship discussions, engineering projects,
                  and selected collaborations.
                </p>

                <div class="profile-list">
                  <div class="profile-row">
                    <span>Base</span>
                    <span>Delhi, India</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="profile-row">
                    <span>Primary Areas</span>
                    <span>Motorsport, CAD, IoT, automotive systems</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="profile-row">
                    <span>Working Style</span>
                    <span>Hands-on, fast-learning, execution-focused</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="profile-row">
                    <span>Open To</span>
                    <span>Teams, sponsors, technical collaborations</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">About</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">A builder’s mindset, shaped by machines.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              A focused overview for teams, sponsors, collaborators, and anyone
              evaluating the work behind the name.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-grid">
            <article class="panel content-card">
              <p>
                My work started with physical curiosity: dismantling, repairing,
                testing, and building RC models, cars, boats, planes, drones,
                and mechanical systems. That foundation grew into CAD design,
                aeromodelling, coding, IoT systems, automotive restoration, and
                motorsport.
              </p>

              <p>
                Today, I combine driving experience with technical depth:
                Formula-4 testing, drift instruction, autocross competition,
                product-facing industry exposure, and self-built hardware
                projects. The common standard across all of it is simple:
                understand the system properly, then improve it.
              </p>

              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Motorsport</span>
                <span class="tag">Mechanical Systems</span>
                <span class="tag">CAD</span>
                <span class="tag">IoT</span>
                <span class="tag">Automotive</span>
                <span class="tag">Climate Advocacy</span>
              </div>
            </article>

            <aside class="panel quote-card">
              <div>
                <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
                <blockquote>
                  The goal is not to look technical. The goal is to build,
                  test, refine, and make the machine better.
                </blockquote>
              </div>

              <p>
                This portfolio will grow into a complete record of projects,
                media, case studies, racing experience, and technical work.
              </p>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="capabilities" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">Capabilities</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Where I create value.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              Four areas connect the profile: driving, mechanics, design, and
              connected systems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="capability-grid">
            <article class="panel capability-card">
              <div class="number">01</div>
              <h3>Motorsport & Driver Development</h3>
              <p>
                Formula-4 testing, drift instruction, autocross competition,
                simulator work, car control, video review, and performance
                iteration.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="panel capability-card">
              <div class="number">02</div>
              <h3>Mechanical & Automotive Work</h3>
              <p>
                Hands-on diagnostics, restoration planning, powertrain
                understanding, workshop problem-solving, and real mechanical
                execution.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="panel capability-card">
              <div class="number">03</div>
              <h3>CAD, Prototyping & Fabrication</h3>
              <p>
                CAD-led development for functional parts, assemblies, brackets,
                housings, airframes, fixtures, and prototype mechanisms.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="panel capability-card">
              <div class="number">04</div>
              <h3>Software, IoT & Control Systems</h3>
